\begin_layout Subsection
费曼参数化
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
费曼参数化基于一些简单的数学公式。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
最简单的是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{AB}=\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\frac{1}{\left[A+(B-A)x\right]^{2}}=\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\dif y\delta(x+y-1)\frac{1}{\left[xA+yB\right]^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

这个等式可以这么理解，首先从量纲上，右边的积分结果一定是
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

的负二次方，结果只可能由
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

和它们的系数组成。积分对
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

是对称的，所以不可能出现类似
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{A}{B}$
\end_inset

的结构，所以只能是
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{n}{AB}$
\end_inset

，然后考虑系数。首先取
\begin_inset Formula $A=B$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A^{2}}\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\dif y\delta(x+y-1)
\]

\end_inset


\series bold
这种类型的积分需要考虑积分区域的变化，因为
\begin_inset Formula $\delta(x)$
\end_inset

函数相当于一个分布，使得积分区间中某些区域不贡献了
\series default
。
\begin_inset Formula $\delta(x)$
\end_inset

函数总是会减少一个维度，因此总相当于积分区域
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

的维度减少，这样我们需要知道降维的积分区域
\begin_inset Formula $D^{\prime}$
\end_inset

的面积，和相对于原来积分测度的伸缩比例。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
比如在二维情况下，
\begin_inset Formula $\delta(x+y-1)$
\end_inset

限定积分区域在
\begin_inset Formula $x+y=1$
\end_inset

的一条支线上，这条直线长度为
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

，直线上的点坐标为
\begin_inset Formula $(x,1-x)$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dif s=\sqrt{\abs{\frac{\partial x}{\partial x}}^{2}+\abs{\frac{\partial(1-x)}{\partial x}}^{2}}\dif x=\sqrt{2}\dif x
\]

\end_inset

与原本低维的积分测度
\begin_inset Formula $\dif x=\dif y$
\end_inset

相比，放大了
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

倍，因此回去的时候要乘以
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}$
\end_inset

，跟长度约掉，刚好为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

。其实有一个更简单的考虑方法，这条线在
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

轴 or 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

轴的投影刚好为
\begin_inset Formula $(0,1)$
\end_inset

。也就是说，满足条件的积分区域对原来低维测度的投影长度为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

，所以直接得到积分区域的低维长度为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

。注意这个投影总是向原点的方向进行的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于高维的情况，
\begin_inset Formula $\delta(x+y+z+\cdots)=1$
\end_inset

。总的测度体积是
\begin_inset Formula $1^{n}=1$
\end_inset

。用积分式表示
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数的限制，可以写成 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\int_{0}^{1}\dif y\int_{0}^{1}\dif z\cdots\delta(x+y+z+\cdots)\to\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\int_{0}^{1-x+\epsilon}\dif y\int_{0}^{1-x-y+\epsilon}\dif z\delta(x+y+z+\cdots)
\]

\end_inset

这个积分表示的是
\begin_inset Formula $n-1$
\end_inset

维单位锥体的体积（各边都相等），
\begin_inset Formula $V=\frac{1}{(n-1)!}$
\end_inset

。所以，一般有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A_{1}A_{2}\cdots A_{n}}=\int_{0}^{1}\dif x_{1}\cdots\dif x_{n}\delta(\sum x_{1}-1)\frac{(n-1)!}{\left[x_{1}A_{1}+\cdots+x_{n}A_{n}\right]^{n}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
类似地，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{AB^{n}}=\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\dif y\delta(x+y-1)\frac{ny^{n-1}}{\left[xA+yB\right]^{n+1}}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{ABC}=\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\dif y\dif z\delta(x+y+z-1)\frac{2}{\left[xA+yB+zC\right]^{3}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
通过这些公式，可以把传播子合并起来，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{1}{k^{2}}\frac{1}{(k-p)^{2}} & =\int\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\frac{1}{\left[k^{2}+x\left((k-p)^{2}-k^{2}\right)\right]^{2}}\\
 & =\int\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\frac{1}{\left[k^{2}-2kxp+xp^{2}\right]^{2}}\\
 & =\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\int\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{1}{\left[(k-xp)^{2}-\Delta\right]^{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

when 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=-p^{2}x(1-x)$
\end_inset

。我们可以通过shift 
\begin_inset Formula $k\to k+xp$
\end_inset

使积分只依赖于
\begin_inset Formula $k^{2}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Schwinger 参数化
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当
\begin_inset Formula $\Im{A}>0$
\end_inset

时：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{i}{A}=\int_{0}^{\infty}\dif se^{isA}\label{eq:b.5}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Im{A}>0$
\end_inset

可以保证积分是良好定义的。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(\frac{i}{A})^{2}=\int_{0}^{\infty}s\dif se^{isA}
\]

\end_inset

可以通过不停求导，得到更多等式。Eq.
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:b.5"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

暗示了
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{1}{AB}=-\int_{0}^{\infty}\dif s\int_{0}^{\infty}\dif te^{isA+itB}\label{eq:b.7}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $\Im{A}>0$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\Im{B}>0$
\end_inset

(也就是用费曼传播子)。Schwinger 参数 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 具有很好的物理解释：
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 是 proper times of the particles as they travel along their paths in the
 Feynman graph。Schwinger proper-time interpretation 见 Chapter 32。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注意如果令
\begin_inset Formula $s+t=\tau$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $x=\frac{t}{s+t}$
\end_inset

,or 
\begin_inset Formula $t=x\tau$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $s=(1-x)\tau$
\end_inset

，Eq.
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:b.7"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

变成
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\frac{1}{AB} & =-\int_{0}^{\infty}\tau\dif\tau\int_{0}^{1}\dif xe^{i\tau(A+Bx-Ax)}\\
 & =\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\frac{1}{\left[A+(B-A)x\right]^{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

所以费曼参数化
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 也有物理意义，as the relative proper time 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{s}{s+t}$
\end_inset

 of the two particles in the loop.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
另外一些有用的等式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{A^{n}B^{m}}=\frac{\Gamma(n+m)}{\Gamma(n)\Gamma(m)}\int_{0}^{\infty}\dif s\frac{s^{m-1}}{(A+Bs)^{n+m}}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{AB}=\int_{0}^{\infty}\dif s\frac{1}{(A+Bs)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

Schwinger paramerters 用于 Chapter 34 and Chapter 35.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Wick rotations
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
做完费曼参数化之后，得到一个在 Minkowski 空间对圈动量的积分。恢复费曼传播子中的
\begin_inset Formula $i\epsilon$
\end_inset

因子，
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

–loop 积分经常是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{1}{(k^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon)^{n}}
\]

\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $k_{0}$
\end_inset

复平面上，积分的极点在二四象限，实轴上的积分和虚轴上的积分是大小相等，符号相反的。所以，令
\begin_inset Formula $k^{2}\to-k_{0}^{2}-\vec{k}^{2}=-k_{E}^{2}$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula $k_{E}^{2}=k_{0}^{2}+\vec{k}^{2}$
\end_inset

是 Euclidean momentum.
 这被称为 Wick rotation。经过 Wick rotation，
\begin_inset Formula $i\varepsilon$
\end_inset

没有用了，我们可以令
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon=0$
\end_inset

。wick转动的最终效果是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{1}{(k^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon)^{n}}\to\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dif^{4}k_{E}}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{i}{(-k_{E}^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon)^{n}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
四维 Euclidean 空间的单位球体表面积为
\begin_inset Formula $\int\dif\Omega_{4}=2\pi^{2}$
\end_inset

。所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dif^{4}k_{E}}{(2\pi)^{4}}f(k_{E}^{2})=\frac{1}{16\pi^{4}}\int\dif\Omega_{4}\int_{0}^{\infty}k_{E}^{3}\dif k_{E}f(k_{E}^{2})=\frac{1}{8\pi^{2}}\int_{0}^{\infty}k_{E}^{3}\dif k_{E}f(k_{E}^{2})
\]

\end_inset

Wick rotation 只是数学技巧，并没有物理内容，只要没有新的 pole 违反回路转动，它就成立。只有在两圈或者多圈图中才会遇到。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
常用公式有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{k^{2}}{(k^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon)^{4}} & =\frac{-i}{48\pi^{2}}\frac{1}{\Delta}\\
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{1}{(k^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon)^{r}} & =\frac{i(-1)^{r}}{16\pi^{2}}\frac{1}{(r-1)(r-2)}\frac{1}{\Delta^{r-2}},r>2\\
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dif^{4}k}{(2\pi)^{4}}\frac{k^{2}}{(k^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon)^{r}} & =\frac{i(-1)^{r-1}}{16\pi^{2}}\frac{2}{(r-1)(r-2)(r-3)}\frac{1}{\Delta^{r-3}},r>3
\end{align*}

\end_inset

等等。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
维数正规化
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在最常用的是维数正规化。key observation is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\frac{\dif^{d}k}{(2\pi)^{d}}\frac{1}{(k^{2}-\Delta+i\varepsilon)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

只有在
\begin_inset Formula $d\geq4$
\end_inset

的时候才是发散的。如果
\begin_inset Formula $d<4$
\end_inset

，它是收敛的。我们可以 Wick rotate，然后把结果解析延拓到
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

维中。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
旋量代数
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

维中，度规矩阵是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g^{\mu\nu}=\text{diag}(1,-1,-1,\cdots,-1),
\]

\end_inset

即使对于非正数
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

，也精确地有一个 timelike dimension。度规矩阵满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g^{\mu\nu}g_{\mu\nu}=d
\]

\end_inset

洛伦兹不变的相空间为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dif\Pi_{\text{LIPS}}\equiv(2\pi)^{d}\prod_{\text{final states }j}\frac{\dif^{d-1}p_{j}}{(2\pi)^{d-1}}\frac{1}{2E_{p_{j}}}\delta^{d}(\sum p)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们可以定义
\begin_inset Formula $d=4-\varepsilon$
\end_inset

时空的旋量代数和
\begin_inset Formula $d=4$
\end_inset

的代数类似。更确切地说，我们假设
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

维时空中，
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \gamma^{\mu},\gamma^{\nu}\right\} =2g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

。旋量空间中的单位矩阵满足
\begin_inset Formula $\tr\mathbbm{1}_{\alpha\beta}=4$
\end_inset

 as in four dimensions。在包含
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{5}$
\end_inset

的理论中，我们假设存在一个矩阵，满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\{ \gamma^{5},\gamma^{\mu}\right\} =0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
具有 anomalies 的理论是唯一可能会有 subtleties 的地方。可参考 [Polchinski 1998, Appendix B]。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
标量积分
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们将使表达式只依赖于
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

的幅度，然后使用
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}\dif^{d}k=\int\dif\Omega_{d}\int k^{d-1}\dif k
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $\dif\Omega_{d}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

维空间单维球体的微分立体角。明确写出来是，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\dif\Omega_{d}=\sin^{d-2}(\phi_{d-1})\dif\phi_{d-1}\sin^{d-3}(\phi_{d-2})\dif\phi_{d-2}\cdots\sin(\phi_{2})\dif\phi_{2}\dif\phi_{1}\label{eq:b.23}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

共有
\begin_inset Formula $d-1$
\end_inset

个角度坐标，
\begin_inset Formula $\dif\phi_{1}$
\end_inset

直接积分，从
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{2}$
\end_inset

开始有
\begin_inset Formula $\sin$
\end_inset

函数，
\begin_inset Formula $\sin(\phi_{2})\dif\phi_{2}$
\end_inset

，后面
\begin_inset Formula $\sin$
\end_inset

的次幂依次升高，最高
\begin_inset Formula $d-2$
\end_inset

次幂。其中
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{i}$
\end_inset

是相对于
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

th 轴的角度。令
\begin_inset Formula $0\leq\phi_{1}\leq2\pi$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $0\leq\phi_{i}<\pi$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $i>1$
\end_inset

。例如，
\begin_inset Formula $\dif\Omega_{2}=\dif\phi$
\end_inset

。对于
\begin_inset Formula $d=3$
\end_inset

，我们一般写成
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{1}=\phi$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{2}=\theta$
\end_inset

 giving
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dif\Omega_{3}=\dif\cos\theta\dif\phi
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

维空间的表面为
\begin_inset Formula $d-1$
\end_inset

维。
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

维单位球的
\begin_inset Formula $d-1$
\end_inset

维表面积为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Omega_{2}=\int\dif\Omega_{2}=2\pi\text{ (circle) },\int\dif\Omega_{3}=4\pi\text{ sphere },\int\dif\Omega_{4}=2\pi^{2}\text{ three-sphere},\cdots,
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

维球的体积为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V_{d}=\Omega_{d}\int_{0}^{R}\dif r\,r^{d-1}=\Omega_{d}\frac{1}{d}R^{d}
\]

\end_inset

which are 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{2}=\pi R^{2},V_{3}=\frac{4}{3}\pi R^{3},V_{4}=\frac{1}{2}\pi^{2}R^{4}$
\end_inset

,etc.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于非整数维，表面积公式可以用类似高斯积分的方法求出：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
(\sqrt{\pi})^{d} & =\left(\int\dif xe^{-x^{2}}\right)^{d}=\int\dif\Omega_{d}\int_{0}^{\infty}\dif r\,r^{d-1}e^{-r^{2}}\\
 & =\int\dif\Omega_{d}\int_{0}^{\infty}\frac{1}{2}(\dif r^{2})\,r^{2(\nicefrac{d}{2}-1)}e^{-r^{2}}\\
 & =\frac{1}{2}\Gamma(\frac{d}{2})\int\dif\Omega_{d}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Omega_{d}=\int\dif\Omega_{d}=\frac{2\pi^{\nicefrac{d}{2}}}{\Gamma(\frac{d}{2})}=2\frac{\pi^{\nicefrac{d}{2}}}{\Gamma(\frac{d}{2})}
\]

\end_inset

也可以选择直接把 Eq.
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:b.23"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 积出来：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Omega_{d} & =2\pi\prod_{n=2}^{d-1}\left(\int_{0}^{\pi}\dif\phi_{n}\sin^{n-1}(\phi_{n})\right)=2\pi\prod_{n=2}^{d-1}\left(-\int_{1}^{-1}\dif\cos(\phi_{n})\left(1-\cos^{2}\phi_{n}\right)^{(n-2)/2}\right)\\
 & =2\pi\prod_{n=2}^{d-1}2\int_{0}^{1}\dif x\left(1-x^{2}\right)^{(n-2)/2}=2\pi\prod_{n=2}^{d-1}\int_{0}^{1}\dif x^{2}\left(1-x^{2}\right)^{(n-2)/2}x^{2(-1/2)}\\
 & =2\pi\prod_{n=2}^{d-1}\beta(\frac{n}{2},\frac{1}{2})=2\pi\prod_{n=2}^{d-1}\frac{\Gamma(\frac{n}{2})\Gamma(\frac{1}{2})}{\Gamma(\frac{n+1}{2})}\\
 & 2\pi\prod_{n=2}^{d-1}\sqrt{\pi}\left(\frac{\Gamma(\frac{n}{2})}{\Gamma(\frac{n+1}{2})}\right)\\
 & =2\pi^{d/2}\frac{\Gamma(\frac{2}{2})}{\Gamma(\frac{3}{2})}\frac{\Gamma(\frac{3}{2})}{\Gamma(\frac{4}{2})}\cdots\frac{\Gamma(\frac{d-1}{2})}{\Gamma(\frac{d}{2})}=2\pi^{d/2}\frac{\Gamma(1)}{\Gamma(\frac{d}{2})}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

Using 
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma(1)=(1-1)!=1$
\end_inset

，回到
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega_{d}=2\frac{\pi^{\nicefrac{d}{2}}}{\Gamma(\frac{d}{2})}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

