伽马函数的四种定义：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma(z)=\int_{0}^{\infty}x^{z-1}e^{-x}\dif x
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma(z)=\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{n^{z}n!}{z(z+1)(z+2)\cdots z(+n)}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma(z)=\frac{1}{z}\prod_{k=1}^{\infty}\frac{\left(1+\frac{1}{k}\right)^{z}}{1+\frac{z}{k}}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{\Gamma(z)}=ze^{\gamma z}\prod_{k=1}^{\infty}\left(1+\frac{z}{k}\right)e^{-\frac{z}{k}}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

是欧拉—马斯克若尼常数（Euler—Mascheroni constant）：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\gamma & =\lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{n=1}^{n}\frac{1}{k}-\ln(n)\\
 & =\frac{1}{1}+\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{3}+\dots+\frac{1}{n}-\ln(n)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

